metadata.name: Serenity
metadata.description:
This is the 1/1 NFT in the collection.

Nature will act on us with all its power only when we bring our humanity into the feeling of it, when our state of mind, our love, our joy or sorrow come into full accord with nature, and it will be impossible to separate the freshness of the morning from the light of our favorite eyes and the gentle sound of the forest from reflections about the life we have lived.

Size: 5887 x 3925px
